overview: Never trust your lawyer! That's the lesson to be learned in New Wave Hookers 3. When Frank takes some friendly advice from his attorney, he ends up losing his wife to a prostitute training center called the Deep House. Not only that, he almost loses his mind. Will Frank ever regain his wife? Or his mind? Will his lawyer charge him for all those phone calls? Hey, it's Dark Bros. movie - what does it matter?
title: New Wave Hookers 3
